description: Captain's Curbside Seafood is serving up some of the best dishes Pennsylvania has ever seen! Coming to you with their delicious Oyster Po' Boys, Ahi Tuna Sandwiches, and Capt'n Chucky's Jumbo Lump Crab Cakes, this is a truck that will never let you down. If you're looking for seafood you can really dig your teeth into, then Captain's Curbside Seafood is the perfect truck for you!
name: Captain's Curbside Seafood
